T02TD1240E:153a-54: aom gha gha gh'a ta ya te dzo r'a pri na ya sh'antim ku ru sv'a h'a //
T02TD1240E:153a-56: aom su pushpa ku le ba le dza la ne sh'antim ku ru sv'a h'a //
T02TD1240E:153a-57: gur kum dang lhan cig ku mu ta'i 'o //
T02TD1240E:153a-58: aom dharme dharm'a r'a dze da ha da ha sarba bighn'am sh'antim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1240E:153a-61: aom ki li su ki li k'a la re ti sarba p'a pam da ha aa mu ka sya sh'intam ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1240E:153a-62: dri zhim pa'i til mar dang lhan cig ka ra b'i ra'i 'o //
T02TD1240E:153a-63: rgyas la aa mra aarka dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-0: kanda pa @153b la bil ba dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-1: au dumw'a ra rdzas lnga rnams //
T02TD1240E:153b-2: sngags pas sngags 'dis sbyin sreg bya //
T02TD1240E:153b-3: aom ga ga ni ga ga na bi lo ki te h'um phat /
T02TD1240E:153b-4: te dzo r'a dza aa mu ka sya pushtim ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1240E:153b-5: kha dog dri dang me yi lce //
T02TD1240E:153b-6: gzugs dang sgra la sogs pa yi //
T02TD1240E:153b-7: yon bdag dge dang mi dge ba //
T02TD1240E:153b-8: sreg blugs bsregs pas me pra brtag / zhi la kha dog dkar 'bar ba //
T02TD1240E:153b-9: rgyas la ser po'i rnam pa ste //
T02TD1240E:153b-10: dbang dang mngon spyod dag la ni //
T02TD1240E:153b-11: dmar dang gnag pa'i me bsngags so //
T02TD1240E:153b-12: dbang po'i gzhu 'dra bzang po ste //
T02TD1240E:153b-13: g-yas su 'khyil ba mchog yin no //
T02TD1240E:153b-14: rdza rnga'i sgra ltar zab pa dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-15: me lce snum zhing rtse gcig bsngags //
T02TD1240E:153b-16: me stag rnam 'phro du ba mang //
T02TD1240E:153b-17: rim gyis ldang zhing khad kyis 'bar //
T02TD1240E:153b-18: mtha' mar rang 'bar gzi brjid can //
T02TD1240E:153b-20: rtse gsum zhib ma 'dra ba nyid //
T02TD1240E:153b-21: de bzhin ba lang mgo 'dra ba //
T02TD1240E:153b-22: de la sogs pa'i mtshan ngan pa //
T02TD1240E:153b-23: mi dge rnams kyang brtag par bya //
T02TD1240E:153b-24: sbyin sreg mtha' ru bsdu ba la //
T02TD1240E:153b-25: me tog spos sogs mchod pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1240E:153b-26: phul te bstod pa 'bar ba'i me //
T02TD1240E:153b-27: tshigs bcad 'di yis gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1240E:153b-28: rang gi don dang gzhan gyi don //
T02TD1240E:153b-29: byin za khyod kyis bsgrubs kyis gshegs //
T02TD1240E:153b-30: de bzhin dus su slar gshegs te //
T02TD1240E:153b-31: bdag gi dngos grub thams cad mdzod //
T02TD1240E:153b-32: 'dis ni ye shes mi dgyes te //
T02TD1240E:153b-33: rdo rje 'chang ba rab tu dgyes //
T02TD1240E:153b-34: rtag pa yi ni rgyal bar dgyes //
T02TD1240E:153b-35: gser gyi mnga' bdag mnyes pa dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-36: padma gar gyi dbang phyug dgyes //
T02TD1240E:153b-37: rta mchog rgyal po dgyes par 'gyur //
T02TD1240E:153b-38: tshangs pa brgya byin dbang phyug che //
T02TD1240E:153b-39: khyab 'jug rlung lha stobs po che //
T02TD1240E:153b-41: zla ba nyi ma gdon gzhan dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-42: sa bdag zhags pa 'dzin pa dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-43: ku be ra dang bden bral dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-44: chos kyi rgyal po dang ni klu //
T02TD1240E:153b-45: dri za lha min mi 'am ci //
T02TD1240E:153b-46: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas pa'i lha //
T02TD1240E:153b-47: 'og min du ni gnas pa dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-48: rgyal po chen po gang gnas dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-49: 'thab bral dang ni dgal ldan na //
T02TD1240E:153b-50: gnas pa yi ni lha rnams dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-51: 'phrul dga' yi ni lha rnams dang //
T02TD1240E:153b-52: de bzhin gzhan 'phrul dbang byed dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-3: mi mjed khams su gnas pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-4: gling bzhir gnas pa'i sems can dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-5: gang zhig khams gsum gnas pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-6: snod dang sems can 'jig rten dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-7: rtsva dang yal ga rtsi shing sogs //
T02TD1240E:154a-8: gang zhig rab dga'i sar gnas dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-9: dri med pha rol phyin pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-11: 'od byed pa na bzhugs pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-12: gang zhig sbyang dkar son pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-13: mngon du gyur pa gang thob dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-14: gang zhig ring song thob pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-15: mi g-yo ba ni non pa dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-16: legs pa'i blo gros la gnas dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-17: gang zhig chos sprin rjes son pa //
T02TD1240E:154a-18: sa bcu'i dbang phyug mgon po rnams //
T02TD1240E:154a-19: de dag thams cad dgyes par 'gyur //
T02TD1240E:154a-20: 'phags pa'i gang zag brgyad po dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-21: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang nyan thos nyid //
T02TD1240E:154a-22: bse ru dang ni tshogs gnas dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-23: dmyal ba yi dags dud 'gro dang //
T02TD1240E:154a-24: lha dang lha ma yin dang mi //
T02TD1240E:154a-25: de ltar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor lo //
T02TD1240E:154a-26: de dag thams cad sbyin sreg gi //
T02TD1240E:154a-28: zhi ba la ni 'o mas mchod //
T02TD1240E:154a-29: rgyas la ser po'i chu yis bsgrub //
T02TD1240E:154a-30: dbang dang mngon spyod dag la ni //
T02TD1240E:154a-31: dmar dang nag po'i chu blugs so //
T02TD1240E:154a-32: zhes bya ba ni me zhi bar bya ba'o //
T02TD1240E:154a-33: sna tshogs rgyud shing las skyes me tog ni //
T02TD1240E:154a-34: dri med sngags dang phyag rgya la sogs te //
T02TD1240E:154a-35: thub dka' zla ba dag gis 'di byas pas //
T02TD1240E:154a-36: 'od mangs 'gro ba'i me tog phreng ltar shog / mkhas pa chen po dpal thub dka' zla bas mdzad pa bzang po yongs su bzung ba zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs so /
T02TD1240E:154a-38: // / legs sbyar rgya mtshor bdag blo goms chung yang //
T02TD1240E:154a-39: 'gro ba mig med ye shes mig thob phyir //
T02TD1240E:154a-40: dkyil 'khor cho ga sngags dang phyag rgya sogs //
T02TD1240E:154a-41: legs bsgyur des ni rig 'dzin rgyal por shog / gzhung 'dir dad dang gzhan phan blos //
T02TD1240E:154a-42: bcos bsgyur gtan la phab bgyis la //
T02TD1240E:154a-43: 'phags pa'i lam ma thob pa'i phyir //
T02TD1240E:154a-44: nongs gyur mkha' 'gro mas bzod mdzod //
